---
title: One-Pot Indian Chicken & Veggie Pilaf with Yoghurt & Parsley
description: One pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take a
chicken and veggie pilaf, the Mumbai and Bengal spices melt into the chicken and rice. One irresistible and easy
dinner coming right up!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
